{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cfc771d283","title":"毛泽东主席接见伊朗左派革命组织代表的谈话记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1f93fdfcb","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"cfc771d283"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jimi","name":"机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"epub","author":"宋永毅","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话.epub"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"jimi":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a2cf6c399d","type":"paragraph","text":"<span class=\"c11\">谈话记录</span>","index":0,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"5f3076be22","type":"paragraph","text":"时　间：1970年10月1日晚10时15分","index":1,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"4ca618bf59","type":"paragraph","text":"地　点：天安门城楼","index":2,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"708e409e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：","index":3,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"e768245ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"伊方—雷兹瓦尼、哈桑、穆哈森","index":4,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"cdc4f2a186","type":"paragraph","text":"中方—林彪、周恩来、康生","index":5,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"ea1768772a","type":"paragraph","text":"翻　译：伍书湖","index":6,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"2824ac97aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（10月1日晚焰火结束后，周恩来总理把代表团引见给毛主席。周总理对毛主席说：“他们是伊朗同志。”毛主席迎上几步同他们亲切地握手。）","index":7,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"5b3a347050","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席（以下简称主席）：伊朗就是波斯，欢迎。","index":8,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"91d7cc316c","type":"paragraph","text":"雷兹瓦尼（以下简称雷）：（用中文高呼）毛主席万岁！","index":9,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"d849386bb1","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（同他们一一握手）谢谢同志们。","index":10,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"78b0c0d688","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：见到毛主席是对我们最大的鼓舞。","index":11,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"bccb4cfcdd","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问康生）他们来多久了？","index":12,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"ce8dfed269","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：一个多月了。","index":13,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"e7da7559e5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们愿意呆多久就呆多久。","index":14,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"82807d46fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”）","index":15,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"f296f138d0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：同志们万岁！同志们好，欢迎你们。","index":16,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"102e609e52","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：能见到您，对我们是最大的鼓舞，我们一定努力做您的好学生。","index":17,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"9208e42a4a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我们都是同志，我们向你们学习。","index":18,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"7da48df4fa","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：毛主席万岁！","index":19,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"542d6b6903","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：谢谢。你们很年轻，未来是属于你们的。我老了，不行了。","index":20,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"0cd01b2675","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷等人笑着摇头，用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”）","index":21,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"bd2db43048","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：祝你们革命胜利！","index":22,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"697867092e","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”毛主席再次同代表团二同志一一握手告别，并向前走了几步微笑着挥手欢送他们。然后，周恩来总理把他们带到林彪面前，林从座位上站起来同他们握手。）","index":23,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"d162f6bd39","type":"paragraph","text":"林：欢迎你们！","index":24,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"93cc34db4e","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：我们看到毛主席和您，是对我们最大的鼓舞，我们一定要按照毛主席的指示办事。","index":25,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"9fb3c17b0a","type":"paragraph","text":"林：你们会逐渐取得革命胜利的。","index":26,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"},{"id":"f5ba852224","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷等同林握手告别，又同周总理握手告别，周总理用英文向他们说“再见”。）<br style=\"clear:both;\">","index":27,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283"}],"page":{"id":"873ae1e3e6","publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"cfc771d283","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}